ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would strongly recommend this class to anyone doing research in vascular biology. I may even audit the class again at the end of my PhD to get an update on the state of the field.
I strongly recommend this course to students who are interested in vascular biology. It will be a big help.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This course improved my biology knowledge to a significant degree and will help me choose a relevant path for my future benchtop studies.

I am in a vascular lab. This course is very helpful in deepening my knowledge of my profession. Additionally, I think this course helps train me in scientific thinking and inspire me how to think about a project in an independent way.
